metadata.name: Evo Card: Fauna Monk of Jalah
metadata.description:
This is a single-use card of the Monk that allows another collector to borrow the evolution utility with a Spirit to create a custom Awakened. 

Original owners of the Monks can lend these cards out without risking their main NFTs.

To use the card it will be sent back to me once we have discussed which Spirit it will be used with. Feel free to DM me any questions you may have before purchasing.

More info on the project: https://www.jeyram.xyz/nft/project-roadmap
